    "summary": "The user expresses profound feelings of inadequacy and parental guilt, eventually suggesting that their death might be a \"responsible\" way to unburden their children. The assistant responds by acknowledging the user's distress and explicitly directing them toward mental health professionals and support systems, warning against drastic measures.",
